	<div class="terms terms-inline"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_248 first"><a href="/categories/information-records" rel="tag" title="Neutral information about a place, group or time. Can be tax records, census data or anything equally boring.">Information &amp; Records</a></li>
